“Slide” was first previewed by Ty Dolla $ign at Le Baroque in Geneva, Switzerland on September 30, 2023. The song, with updated production, was then previewed twice by Fred again.. on November 4, 2023, at a DJ set in Los Angeles. He spoke on his involvement in the song;

"This is madness for me, I made this with my brother Ty a few months ago"

The song was performed in full at the “Vultures Rave” in Miami on December 12, 2023, and used in an advertisement for the YZY PODS on December 28, 2023. <a href="http://www.last.fm/music/%C2%A5$/_/Slide">Read more on Last.fm</a>.
